  "url": "https://www.tamilmirror.lk/\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd/\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd-\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd-\u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4-\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1-\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd-\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd-\u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1/175-301120",
  "time_ut": 1658771480,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A Polish national who was in jail in Sri Lanka was arrested in Tamil Nadu",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A Polish national has been arrested for illegally traveling to Tamil Nadu from Sri Lanka by sea.",
        "Inquiries conducted on the arrested person revealed that he had been arrested in Sri Lanka for an offense related to criminal activity and was released after completing his sentence.",
        "A boat was recovered yesterday (24) in a state of disrepair in the Munangadu area near Vedaranyam, Tamil Nadu.",
        "The boat in question is an inflatable boat (like a balloon). It is designed to accommodate two people.",
        "Apart from this, some items such as shoes used by whirlpools, pump to fill the boat with air, jacket, glasses used by whirlpools in the sea, more than 18 water bottles and floating bags have also been recovered from near the boat.",
        "The Coast Guard of Tamil Nadu suspected that the boat might have entered Tamil Nadu from Sri Lanka, and various parties such as the Coast Guard and the Q Squad carried out intensive investigations.",
        "With the help of sniffer dogs and Tron cameras, intensive surveillance was carried out in the areas.",
        "At that time, the police rushed to Arukatu area near Vedaranyam area and arrested him based on the information received that a foreign national was moving in a suspicious manner.",
        "He was arrested on charges of illegally entering Tamil Nadu without a passport from Sri Lanka after the investigations conducted on him revealed that he was from Poland."
      ],
